4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive Data Science & Machine Learning course designed for beginners with no prior experience. Over 16 weeks, students will learn Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics, equipping them to become Data Analysts. The curriculum covers predictive modeling, data algorithms, and real-life case problem-solving, along with industry-standard tools. Classes are conducted thrice a week with a maximum of 12 students per class. Upon completion, participants receive recognized certificates. The course is available in both English and Spanish. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop